00:18.732 --> 00:21.317
<font color="#808080">NARRATOR:</font> <i>The universe...</i>

00:21.417 --> 00:24.393
<i>So full of wonders...</i>

00:24.739 --> 00:28.685
<i>I could spend hours and hours
looking up at the sky.</i>

00:29.087 --> 00:33.348
<i>So many stars,
so many mysteries...</i>

00:34.768 --> 00:37.598
<i>And there's one very special star</i>

00:37.733 --> 00:41.739
<i>that makes me think
of one very special person.</i>

00:43.318 --> 00:45.493
<i>Now let me tell you my story.</i>

00:47.002 --> 00:48.956
<i>At the dawn of time,</i>

00:49.325 --> 00:50.897
<i>from the chaos,</i>

00:51.061 --> 00:53.248
<i>came an exception.</i>

00:53.798 --> 00:58.056
<i>One of the most mysterious secrets
of the universe.</i>

00:59.038 --> 01:03.117
<i>You see, I come from
that very mysterious and unique place.</i>

01:03.331 --> 01:09.087
<i>We are the only known solar system
with double gravity.</i>

01:09.304 --> 01:13.764
<i>Two twin planets
whirling together around one sun</i>

01:13.864 --> 01:17.753
<i>but each with its own
and opposite gravity.</i>

01:18.314 --> 01:22.419
<i>Now, in our world
it's possible to fall up</i>

01:22.519 --> 01:25.461
<i>and to rise down.</i>

01:26.057 --> 01:29.613
<i>But... my story,
it's about love.</i>

01:30.280 --> 01:34.408
<i>Some people say
that true lovers are one soul</i>

01:34.508 --> 01:36.818
<i>that is separated when it's born.</i>

01:36.947 --> 01:42.035
<i>And those two halves will always yearn
to find their way back together.</i>

01:42.526 --> 01:45.321
<i>Well, to understand my story,</i>

01:45.450 --> 01:50.035
<i>you're gonna need to know the three
basic laws of double gravity.</i>

01:50.444 --> 01:54.000
<i>All matter, every single object</i>

01:54.100 --> 01:59.088
<i>is pulled by the gravity of the world that
it comes from, and not the other.</i>

01:59.334 --> 02:04.435
<i>An object's weight can be offset using
matter from the opposite world:</i>

02:04.522 --> 02:06.826
<i>inverse-matter.</i>

02:06.995 --> 02:08.715
<i>The problem is:</i>

02:08.815 --> 02:13.978
<i>After a few hours of contact,
matter in contact with inverse-matter</i>

02:14.120 --> 02:15.620
<i>...burns.</i>

02:18.002 --> 02:21.300
<i>All these laws are as old
as the universe itself.</i>

02:21.435 --> 02:25.885
<i>They're are unchangeable,
and there are no exceptions.</i>

02:26.973 --> 02:28.809
<i>Gravity...</i>

02:29.523 --> 02:32.261
<i>They say you can't fight it.</i>

02:32.478 --> 02:35.090
<i>Well, I disagree.</i>

02:35.219 --> 02:39.348
<i>What if love
was stronger than gravity?</i>

02:40.927 --> 02:43.886
<i>Now let's go back
to the dark times</i>

02:44.174 --> 02:48.378
<i>when any contact between worlds
was extremely dangerous</i>

02:48.478 --> 02:51.629
<i>and totally forbidden.</i>

02:54.624 --> 02:58.156
<i>Up top had grown rich
and prosperous</i>

02:58.256 --> 03:00.753
<i>while here, down below,</i>

03:00.853 --> 03:05.934
<i>we stole inverse-metal from up top
to heat our homes and to survive</i>

03:06.309 --> 03:08.823
<i>risking everything,</i>

03:08.923 --> 03:10.730
<i>even our own lives.</i>

03:10.830 --> 03:12.730
I think he's dead.

03:24.391 --> 03:27.468
Hey! Police!

03:29.959 --> 03:35.363
<i>They only authorized contact
between worlds is through TransWorld,</i>

03:35.608 --> 03:38.174
<i>a giant corporation up top,</i>

03:38.261 --> 03:41.328
<i>created to take cheap oil
from down below</i>

03:41.428 --> 03:44.790
<i>and to sell back to us
overpriced electricity</i>

03:44.890 --> 03:47.282
<i>that we couldn't afford.</i>

03:53.247 --> 03:57.399
<i>Because of TransWorld,
I grew up in an orphanage.</i>

03:57.610 --> 04:00.481
<i>You see,
my parents died in the Big Blast,</i>

04:00.581 --> 04:06.382
<i>a TransWorld oil refinery explosion
that destroyed much of the city.</i>

04:07.844 --> 04:10.757
<i>Fortunately,
there were the weekends.</i>

04:11.318 --> 04:14.217
<i>They let me visit
my great aunt Becky,</i>

04:14.441 --> 04:16.406
<i>my only surviving relative.</i>

04:17.201 --> 04:21.833
<font color="#D900D9">(SLOW ORCHESTRAL VIOLIN MUSIC)</font>

04:37.717 --> 04:42.817
